CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Yunji Inc is a social e-commerce platform in China that offers a membership-based model that leverages the power of social interaction. The company provides a host of selected commodities such as beauty and personal care, mobile phones and digital products, baby and maternal products, toys, fruits, and other fresh products. Geographically, the firm operates in China.
